{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were able to do a lot of things with their food and get favors with their findings, even between the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, in July of 1944, I did not hear no orchestra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard about the orchestra later, but I did not hear the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least, at that day, when I arrived, it was just the guards outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw some dogs-- holding some dogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But only the prisoners who orders us around already in a uniform, ordered us around into groups.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leave your packages, and all kinds-- my-- my mother spoke German, understood German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I just followed, or-- followed the group, whichever direction they pushed me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I didn't speak any German at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I learned quickly the necessary words, what I was supposed to know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That when it's appel, you have to run outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they ordered me around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- anyway, I was working in the kitchen, at one location, and I was talking to the next fellow to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't hear the guard, the SS guard, yelling at me, shut up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he picked up a pitchfork, which we shoveled the-- the-- the cabbage into the containers to make sauerkraut, and threw it at me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It went through my right foot, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was injured.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a few days later, I wasn't able to stand on my foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And by then I knew-- it was already three and a half or so months I'd been in Auschwitz-- that a limping Jew is a dead Jew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this encampment where I was, there was a so-called hospital barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wasn't much, but at least I was able to get off of my-- they ordered me into the hospital barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
